{"data":[{"date":"15:19 30/07","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda\u2019 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng 30/7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/7, trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1edbt lo h\u01a1n b\u1edfi \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/20180729-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-vui-tu-dinh-trong-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young. B\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho Park Ji Sung v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh. \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng b\u1ecb tr\u00e0n d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f9ng c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n n\u00ean trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 1 th\u00e1ng r\u01b0\u1ee1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Ju Young sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y, h\u00f4m nay \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. B\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay\u00a030/7, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ghi h\u00ecnh kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng trong kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh, m\u00e1y ghi h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn cho th\u1ea7y Park cho th\u1ea5y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1ee9c ph\u00ed b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1807","checkdouble":"192323"},{"date":"15:22 30/07","title":"Sao x\u1eb9t l\u1ea1c quan v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/31/sao-xet-lac-quan-voi-khoi-dau-moi-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson Palmieri h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm Emerson Palmieri t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c g\u00ec trong n\u1eeda n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Hau-ve-Emerson-Palmieri-da-san-sang-tro-lai-thi-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Emerson c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Emerson c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, anh l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 kh\u00ed th\u1ebf h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i: \u201cQuan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung m\u00e3n c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cSarri ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang th\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t lu\u1ed3ng gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Napoli c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 \u00fd th\u1ee9c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ra sao. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u0129nh h\u1ed9i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Sarri, \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Arsenal v\u00e0 Lyon, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh v\u1edbi Man City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1806","checkdouble":"192324"},{"date":"15:39 30/07","title":"V\u00e9 xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng: VFF \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 4.0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ve-xem-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-vff-ap-dung-cong-nghe-40.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele</h2>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Giam-doc-the-thao-Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i Camp Nou\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c \u2018bom t\u1ea5n\u2019 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e0y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Barca.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao CLB,\u00a0Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea5n an ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ef1u sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Dembele s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Dembele s\u1ebd ra \u0111i sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, k\u00e9m xa so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi anh c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span>\u00a0t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele.Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bartomeu c\u0169ng t\u1eebng\u00a0kh\u0103ng kh\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u00a0\"Dembele s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u1edf Camp Nou.\u00a0C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Coutinho l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn lao trong c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOusmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Barca \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Anh l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Barca t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (sau Neymar). Tuy nhi\u00ean cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, CLB Barcelona v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/17/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Monchi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<em style=\"outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family:\" new=\"\" windowtext=\"\" none=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></em></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1805","checkdouble":"192325"},{"date":"15:38 30/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP PSG vs Atletico Madrid 18h35 ng\u00e0y 30/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/psg-vs-atletico-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u PSG vs Atletico gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Internationl Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 18h35 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN</h2>\r\nPSG: H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 World Cup nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Di Maria ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung.<br>\r\nAtletico: V\u1eafng Costa, Saul, Koke, Godin, Giminez v\u00e0 Filipe.<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, PSG thua c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Atletico th\u1eafng 6 v\u00e0 thua 2 \u1edf 8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn PSG thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Buffon. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Lemar, Rodri hay Gelson.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/nhan-dinh-psg-vs-atletico-madrid-18h35-ngay-307-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>PH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U</h2>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel (PSG): \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n h\u01a1n khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\".<br>\r\nHLV Diego Simeone (Atletico): \"Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 PSG tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c\",<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. 3/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng n\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Atletico 1-1 (pen 3-1) Arsenal (ICC 2018) </strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Atletico-1-1-Arsenal.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1804","checkdouble":"192326"},{"date":"16:29 30/07","title":"Ibra c\u00f3 hattrick \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ibra-co-hattrick-dau-tien-tren-dat-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap LA Galaxy l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 4-3.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIbra ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1-0, r\u1ed3i 2-1, Orlando City \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc LA Galaxy khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 show di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic. Ph\u00fat 47, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Dos Santos, g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Anh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng 3-3 sau khi Dom Dwyer gi\u00fap Orlando v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 phim kinh d\u1ecb n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u1edf ph\u00fat 71, khi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u00e0y tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 chung cu\u1ed9c cho LA Galaxy. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00fa hattrick \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ibra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 26/2/2017 (M.U 3-0 Saint-Etienne).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick gi\u00fap LA Galaxy th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 4-3\" title=\"Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/ibra-co-hattrick-dau-tien-tren-dat-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick gi\u00fap LA Galaxy th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t&nbsp;th\u1edf 4-3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Anh c\u0169ng gi\u00fap LA Galaxy n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 9, v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1edd \u0110\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a MLS, ch\u1ec9 sau Los Angeles FC v\u00e0 Dallas FC.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man United, v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Mourinho h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 MLS, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ibrahimovic l\u1eadp hattrick l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 anh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Ibra - Wayne Rooney c\u0169ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft DC United (\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c b\u1edd T\u00e2y) v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-dau-tien-cua-rooney-trong-mau-ao-dc-united-331-192328.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ban-thang-dau-tien-cua-rooney-trong-mau-ao-dc-united.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-dau-tien-cua-rooney-trong-mau-ao-dc-united-331-192328.html\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Rooney trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o DC United</span><br>\r\nSau b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Audi Field, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibrahimovic-mu-can-phai-gianh-danh-hieu-mua-nay-172-192149.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/ibrahimovic-mu-can-phai-gianh-danh-hieu-mua-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibrahimovic-mu-can-phai-gianh-danh-hieu-mua-nay-172-192149.html\">Ibrahimovic: MU c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ibrahimovic cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1803","checkdouble":"192327"},{"date":"16:56 30/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: \u0110\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/giam-doc-the-thao-barca-chot-tuong-lai-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele</h2>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Giam-doc-the-thao-Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i Camp Nou\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c \u2018bom t\u1ea5n\u2019 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e0y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Barca.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao CLB,\u00a0Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea5n an ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ef1u sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Dembele s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Dembele s\u1ebd ra \u0111i sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, k\u00e9m xa so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi anh c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span>\u00a0t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Barca c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele.Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bartomeu c\u0169ng t\u1eebng\u00a0kh\u0103ng kh\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u00a0\"Dembele s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u1edf Camp Nou.\u00a0C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Coutinho l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn lao trong c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOusmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Barca \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Anh l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Barca t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (sau Neymar). Tuy nhi\u00ean cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, CLB Barcelona v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/17/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Monchi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<em style=\"outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family:\" new=\"\" windowtext=\"\" none=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></em></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1802","checkdouble":"192331"},{"date":"16:56 30/07","title":"Harry Maguire: M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a MU ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/harry-maguire-muc-tieu-65-trieu-bang-cua-mu-chat-luong-nhu-the-nao.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. V\u1eady ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Maguire \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Leicester, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/MU-muon-mua-Harry-Maguire-Dat-xat-ra-mieng!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League 2017/18 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1m94, Harry Maguire ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Trung b\u00ecnh anh kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 3,1 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn, cao nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1.500 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Maguire c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh c\u00f3 51 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh to l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng Maguire l\u1ea1i di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t linh ho\u1ea1t, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh c\u00f2n b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/MU-muon-mua-Harry-Maguire-Dat-xat-ra-mieng-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maguire \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Harry Maguire \u0111\u00e3 33 l\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Maguire c\u00f3 9 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u1ee9 treo b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m l\u00e0 b\u1ecb Maguire ph\u00e1 ra b\u1eb1ng s\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng, tranh ch\u1ea5p mi\u1ec5n ch\u00ea, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t hay, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leicester \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Maguire v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a MU&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maguire dang la muc tieu so 1 cua MU\" title=\"Maguire \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/maguire.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maguire \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Maguire so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u00f3 44 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Smalling (22), b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Bailly, Jones v\u00e0 Lindelof c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 s\u1edf h\u1eefu 168 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng, h\u01a1n 34 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi Smalling, v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Bailly (53), Jones (89) v\u00e0 Lindelof&nbsp; (67). Harry Maguire c\u00f3 26 l\u1ea7n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Smalling (17), Phil Jones (14), Lindelof (10) v\u00e0 Bailly (5).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Maguire \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 13 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Smalling, Bailly, Jones v\u00e0 Lindelof ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00f3 6 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18 (bao g\u1ed3m 2 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o), Smalling, Bailly, Jones c\u00f9ng Lindelof kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u00e0o v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City muon co Maguire\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Maguire\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/mu-nhan-tin-buon-tu-muc-tieu-so-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Maguire v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, Maguire t\u1ecf ra l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Maguire lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Theo \u0111\u00f3 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, Maguire l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t (tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ho\u1eb7c g\u00f3c) b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tam s\u01b0, cao nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire</span> v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. V\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1801","checkdouble":"192335"},{"date":"17:10 30/07","title":"M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Khi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, 0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (t\u00ednh trong 90 ph\u00fat) \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eeb s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t th\u00eam 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t l\u00e0 Ander Herrera v\u00e0 Eric Bailly v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eafn r\u0103ng&hellip; v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu, khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Chris Smalling ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. Herrera, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f2n&hellip; c\u0103ng h\u01a1n ch\u1eb7ng &ldquo;Tourmalet&rdquo; d\u1ecbp Gi\u00e1ng sinh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u1ea3nh 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Herrera v\u00e0 Bailly</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 c\u01b0\u1edbp m\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t danh s\u00e1ch d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Jones, Young, Rashford, Valencia, Shaw, Pogba, Lukaku, Fellaini, Matic,&hellip; v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Martial &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi quay v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 &ldquo;h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00ea&rdquo; v\u00e0 m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ecf ra ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 vui v\u1ebb n\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng, khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y&rdquo;. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u00e1m ch\u1ec9, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Milan c\u00f3 16-17 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Liverpool c\u0169ng v\u1eady, c\u00f2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 10&rdquo; &ndash; l\u1eddi Ander Herrera, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh n\u00e0y&hellip; g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y d\u00f9 sao c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0ng Mourinho l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng cho l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf!</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ch\u00ednh Jose Mourinho khi\u1ebfn MU g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Goc-nhin-Chinh-Jose-Mourinho-khien-MU-gap-khung-hoang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khong-hai-long-voi-bld-mu-ve-ke-hoach-mua-sam-172-192248.html\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\r\nMourinho li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o,</span> n\u00f3i ra h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 CLB ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Anthony Martial d\u00f9 anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool,&hellip; r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed7i M.U c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t BL\u0110 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m, r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi \u00f4ng c\u1ed1 t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1eadu b\u00e9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2u. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao thi \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn, h\u1ecd l\u1eafng nghe b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y&rdquo;</em> &ndash; l\u1eddi Pep Guardiola v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man City &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m M.U, <strong>m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1eb9&rdquo; v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn n\u00f3i, tr\u1eadn thua kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch thua. Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua, th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u00f2n nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. H\u00e3y ngh\u0129 xem, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u00f4i m\u00e0!</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t gh\u1ebf cao nh\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/mourinho-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh Jose Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ed Woodward<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant l\u00e0 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp Old Trafford m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, 2 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng (ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00e1 gi\u00e0). Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u0169 trang v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, M.U r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Unai Emery, Man xanh b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng kh\u1ee7ng Mahrez, trong khi Liverpool th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua Tottenham th\u00edch gi\u1eef si\u00eau sao h\u01a1n mua s\u1eafm, ch\u1ec9 Chelsea l\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y &ndash; v\u1edbi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Ed Woodward\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/mou.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho v\u00e0 Ed Woodward d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n 5 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn (kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh Grant). \u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd 2 ch\u1eef k\u00fd t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 1 th\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf - khi PCT Ed Woodward d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <strong>&ldquo;M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 hay \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n&rdquo;.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t (Pep Guardiola), \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 (Ed Woodward), Mourinho c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3. \u00d4ng \u0111ang \u0111i sai h\u01b0\u1edbng, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm n\u1ebfu k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn n\u00f3i, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong kh\u00e2u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb, l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau-172-192298.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau-172-192298.html\">Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 IC Cup sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho&hellip; Martial</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u1eafng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-mua-bong-thu-3-cua-mourinho-thanh-bai-tai-pogba-172-192011.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/MU-nhan-duoc-de-nghi-133-trieu-bang-Anh-cho-tien-ve-Paul-Pogba--hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-mua-bong-thu-3-cua-mourinho-thanh-bai-tai-pogba-172-192011.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u1edf M.U: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Pogba</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y &ndash; b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch Mourinho \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi Pogba, r\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1800","checkdouble":"192337"},{"date":"17:49 30/07","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/4-dieu-mourinho-can-lam-de-cuu-van-tour-du-dau-tham-hoa-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng 90 ph\u00fat trong khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u0103n ra ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Luke Shaw\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/4-dieu-Mourinho-can-lam-de-cuu-van-tour-du-dau-he-2018-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb HLV\u00a0Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Luke Shaw trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC 2018. V\u00e0 x\u00e9t theo ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Ashley Young v\u00e0 Luke Shaw cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i khi \u0111\u1ed5i sang chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 3-5-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn h\u01a1n v\u00e0o Shaw. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y anh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. N\u1ebfu l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, Shaw \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Luke Shaw.</div>\r\n<h2>Mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 cho Sanchez\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/4-dieu-Mourinho-can-lam-de-MU-khong-roi-vao-tham-hoa-o-dau-mua-giai-moi-201819-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u1ea3 hai nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sanchez trong vai tr\u00f2 \u201cs\u1ed1 9\u201d. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi kh\u00e1 nhanh v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Sanchez c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Sanchez c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111e d\u1ecda h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c Sanchez d\u00e2ng cao c\u0169ng gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, b\u1eaft Sanchez ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho Andreas Pereira\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira\" title=\"Andreas Pereira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/174522-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Andreas Pereira ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pereira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u0103ng l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Pereira tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e2ng cao. Fred c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thay Pereira \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Matic b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i to\u00e1n nan gi\u1ea3i. HLV Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. V\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xoay quanh Pereira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ec3 Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fosu-Mensah\" title=\"Fosu-Mensah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fosu-Mensah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Matteo Darmian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean. V\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00f9ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2, Mourinho n\u00ean d\u00f9ng Darmian trong vai tr\u00f2 trung v\u1ec7 l\u1ec7ch bi\u00ean. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c. Eric Bailly c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Darmian trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Darmian, Mourinho n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Timothy Fosu-Mensah. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Antonio Valencia. Fosu-Mensah c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Mourinho mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Luke Shaw, Fosu-Mensah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean. So v\u1edbi Darmian, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Fosu-Mensah s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng Mourinho h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-maguire-muc-tieu-65-trieu-bang-cua-mu-chat-luong-nhu-the-nao-172-192335.html\">Harry Maguire: M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a MU ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho-172-192306.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u201cdanh s\u00e1ch \u0111en\u201d c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1799","checkdouble":"192341"},{"date":"18:00 30/07","title":"5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u2018bom t\u1ea5n\u2019 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Barca h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/14/5-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-voi-barca-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a NHM. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Nou Camp trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>5. Hirving Lozano<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a CLB Barcelona.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hirving Lozano, ng\u00f4i sao n\u0103m nay 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico, thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c, t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia Mexico d\u00f9 m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. Anh hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 PSV Eindhoven t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia H\u00e0 Lan. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 17 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 29 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Lozano, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Lia \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean CLB PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Barca d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u euro, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/5-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-Barca-co-the-xay-ra-he-nay-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Willian<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Willian \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 Messi v\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u1ec1u b\u01b0\u1edbc sang b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua Willian l\u1ea7n 3 t\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean The Blues v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1edd \u01a1. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u2018m\u1eb7n m\u00e0\u2019 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp sang tu\u1ed5i 30 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Willian \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 M.U, Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u2018l\u00e0m gi\u00e1\u2019.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian roi san nhuong vi tri cho Firmino\" title=\"Willian r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Firmino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-237-vuot-mat-mu-barca-sap-no-bom-tan-tu-chelsea.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Adrien Rabiot<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho ra \u0111i, CLB Barcelona \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Nou Camp m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 Adrien Rabiot l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Blaugrana nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Rabiot \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a PSG. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 47 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Tuchel l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i PSG, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi HLV Tuchel mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Draxler \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Marco Verratti v\u00e0 Thiago Motta, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u00f4n Rabiot. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Rabiot ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rabiot\" title=\"Rabiot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/8/hlv-tuchel-giuc-rabiot-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Thiago<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thiago Alcantara chia tay Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2013 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u00e0n anh Xavi- Iniesta.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn b\u1edfi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi Bayern Munich, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o La Masia n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c khan hi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Thiago. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 70 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Thiago, trong khi Barca ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd tr\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thiago alcantara\" title=\"thiago alcantara\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-197-phot-lo-mu-sao-bayern-tinh-tai-ngo-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>1. Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barcelona trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft Barcelona s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1ea5y Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u201cm\u1ed3i nh\u1eed\u201d Chelsea nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Chelsea m\u01b0\u1ee3n Dembele v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hazard.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/hazard-toi-real-madrid-la-giac-mo-cua-moi-cau-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 Barcelona l\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 Hazard qu\u00e1 cao. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1798","checkdouble":"192342"},{"date":"09:30 30/07","title":"Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Leicester City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai ng\u00f4i sao ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Leicester City \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u0103m tia <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\" target=\"_blank\">Harry Maguire</span> v\u00e0 Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leicester kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire v\u00e0 Schmeichel cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leicester kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire v\u00e0 Schmeichel cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leicester kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire v\u00e0 Schmeichel cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi Chelsea, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c chia tay Thibaut Courtois v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Schmeichel s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u trong khung g\u1ed7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu trung v\u1ec7 th\u00e9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn tin kh\u00f4ng vui t\u1eeb Leicester City khi HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea3 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 h\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ea3 Kasper v\u00e0 Harry \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c tr\u1ee5c x\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i, k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed1c s\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot World Cup kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra gi\u00e1 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nTheo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, CLB Man United m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1797","checkdouble":"192295"},{"date":"10:04 30/07","title":"HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng, b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec5n h\u00e0ng hot World Cup sang Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-barca-len-tieng-bo-ngo-kha-nang-tien-mina-sang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yerry Mina c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Anh, Ba Lan v\u00e0 Senegal.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Mina x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u01a1n \u1edf Camp Nou sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra s\u00e2n. Kh\u00f4ng, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palmeiras l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca b\u00e1n Mina cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Valverde b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca b\u00e1n Mina cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-barca-len-tieng-bo-ngo-kha-nang-tien-mina-sang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u00e1n Mina cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi ghi b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t th\u00f4i. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. T\u00f4i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu Barca \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e1n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Mina, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n cho Man Utd, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Harry Maguire hay Toby Alderweireld. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to \u0111\u1ebfn 1m94 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong tranh ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn h\u1eb3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca-180-191127.html\">Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e1\u201d kh\u1ecfi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/man-united-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-nguoi-thua-cua-barca-187-192031.html\">Man United b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span>\u00a0</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1796","checkdouble":"192296"},{"date":"10:10 30/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Petr Cech","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tan-binh-19-trieu-bang-len-tieng-canh-bao-petr-cech.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow l\u00fac 22h00 ng\u00e0y 30/7(V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Nga 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 307 V\u0110QG Nga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 307 V\u0110QG Nga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Ufa-vs-Lokomotiv-Moscow.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede ngay v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Ufa \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Lokomotiv Moscow n\u00ean k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Ufa c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ufa \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng c\u00f3 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thua t\u1edbi 5. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Ufa c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y khi th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Domzale (Slovenia) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 Europa League. L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Ufa ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 0-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Lokomotiv Moscow kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 sau 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Nga, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Yuri Semin c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, Lokomotiv Moscow \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLokomotiv Moscow nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Neftyanik khi 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y th\u1ea5p khi m\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n* 11 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1eeba qua, Ufa th\u1eafng 4, Lokomotiv Moscow th\u1eafng 5, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2<br>\r\n* Lokomotiv Moscow th\u1eafng 2/3 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ufa<br>\r\n* 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc , Ufa \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lokomotiv Moscow<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nUfa: Yerkebulan Seidakhmet kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Vyacheslav Krotov ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\nLokomotiv Moscow: C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1795","checkdouble":"192297"},{"date":"10:33 30/07","title":"Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 IC Cup sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, Man Utd g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o. &quot;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a Club America, San Jose Earthquakes v\u00e0 AC Milan (kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u). M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1eadm Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-4.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, Jose Mourinho h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u0169i d\u00f9i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u00eda. &quot;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&quot; ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool, t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9,...<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Man Utd vs Liverpool, s\u00e2n Michigan \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ebfn 101.254 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i (37.776, 32.549 v\u00e0 21.742). \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u01a1n, Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd: &quot;B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ec3 xem nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u00e9, t\u00f4i xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u1edbi Inter Milan tr\u00ean TV&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t v\u1eafng. C\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 h\u1ecd y\u00eau. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Ander Herrera v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 g\u1eb7p Real Madrid (7h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8) v\u00e0 Bayern Munich (1h15 ng\u00e0y 6/8).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup-172-192295.html\">Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/luke-shaw-tiet-lo-su-that-ve-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-172-192210.html\">Luke Shaw ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-icc-2018-dem-nay-372-192208.html\">MU 1-4 Liverpool: Shaqiri ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, The Klopp b\u1eafn tan x\u00e1c b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-man-utd-bi-ghet-nhat-trong-so-cac-doi-bong-o-premier-league-172-192172.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Man Utd b\u1ecb gh\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-liverpool-tin-mu-se-khong-vao-noi-top-4-mua-giai-nay-172-192118.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool tin MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o n\u1ed5i top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-an-dinh-so-ao-cho-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-192109.html\">Man Utd \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o cho t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1794","checkdouble":"192298"},{"date":"10:15 30/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 30/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-3007.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 30/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-3007-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Digne s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf sao ng\u1ed7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Rabiot, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a PSG. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Blaugrana s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecfi mua Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, ph\u00eda M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes c\u1ee7a Barca. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-3007-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ousmane Dembele r\u1eddi Camp Nou</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-192253.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-192253.html\">HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</span><br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, theo The Sun, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal thay Rabiot</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Ousmane Dembele \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song Arsenal v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n Dembele m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, n\u1ebfu anh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca chot tuong lai Vermaelen\" title=\"Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Vermaelen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Vermaelen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 trung v\u1ec7 Thomas Vermaelen ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Domingos Quina c\u1ee7a West Ham. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sang London \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1793","checkdouble":"192299"}]}